terus mendapat dorongan.

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:30.080
Menakjubkan!

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:33.600
Setiap gadis harus berani
dan berani seperti Anda.

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:34.600
Teman-teman!

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:40.160
Kenapa dia memanggilku jus pare?

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:45.600
Sajeeri, karena jus pare memang

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:48.400
pahit tapi baik
untuk kesehatan ya?

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:49.840
Begitulah keadaanmu.

00:13:50.400 --> 00:13:53.560
Ngomong-ngomong, mereka
menyebutmu pemberani.

00:13:53.760 --> 00:13:56.080
Artinya berani.  - Wow!

